    public class JavaCodeReverseInJobHandler
extends AbstractExecuteInJobHandler
implements org.eclipse.core.commands.IHandler
    A IHandler to start Java Code reverse. The current selection is retrieved. For each selected element, try to reverse it to UML if it correspond to Java code.

    2.0
